## 3. 🌐 Missing Security Headers (OWASP A05)

**Severity: High**

No security headers are set. This leaves the app vulnerable to clickjacking, MIME sniffing, XSS via reflected content, and information disclosure (Express version is advertised by default).

**Fix — Add `helmet`:**
```js
const helmet = require('helmet');
app.use(helmet()); // Sets X-Frame-Options, X-Content-Type-Options, HSTS, CSP, etc.

// Also hide the X-Powered-By header explicitly
app.disable('x-powered-by');
```

