  console.log('HTTPS server running on port 443');
});
```

---

### 10. 🟡 Hardcoded Data and No Pagination (OWASP A02)

The `/users` endpoint returns a hardcoded array. When this is replaced by a real database query, the full table could be returned without limits — both a performance issue and a data-exposure risk.

**Fix – Always paginate and project only required fields at the database layer:**

```js
